{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"这次见了毛主席","authors":["黄玲"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄玲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(编者按)这首诗的作者黄玲，是河南上蔡县的农民诗人，原来她是一个文盲，大跃进后才脱盲的。这首诗是她参加这次文代会，见到了毛主席后写的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月廿三日子好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风吹暖百花芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀，我们见到了您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐的泪花盈眼眶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席频频把手扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢声掌声雷似的响；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然看酸了眼，鼓痛了掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也表不尽我们热爱领袖的衷肠。"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}